text: Henri Demiéville (1888 - 23 November 1956) was a Swiss swimmer. He competed in the men's 400 metre breaststroke event at the 1920 Summer Olympics and the water polo at the 1920 and 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1888 births Category:1956 deaths Category:Swiss male swimmers Category:Swiss male water polo players Category:Olympic swimmers of Switzerland Category:Olympic water polo players of Switzerland Category:Swimmers at the 1920 Summer Olympics Category:Water polo players at the 1920 Summer Olympics Category:Water polo players at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing Category:Male breaststroke swimmers
